# Zathura key bindings

## Mappings
map + zoom in
map - zoom out

# Toggle between light and dark mode
map i recolor

map <C-q> quit

#map b adjust window best-fit



## Unmappings

### Encourage vim-style motions
unmap <PageUp>
unmap <PageDown>
unmap <Home>
unmap <End>

unmap = # causes unintention zoom reset

unmap r # mostly unused

unmap <C-r>  # originaly bound to color inversion
map <C-r> rotate
